# CreatorDNA Core

## Start Here

1. [docs/STATUS.md](../docs/STATUS.md) — next task
2. [docs/tasks/BACKLOG.md](../docs/tasks/BACKLOG.md) — pick unblocked `todo`
3. [docs/development/agent-playbook.md](../docs/development/agent-playbook.md)

Constitution: [AGENTS.md](../AGENTS.md). V1 launch gates: [docs/product/launch-criteria.md](../docs/product/launch-criteria.md).

## V1 Scope

- **Platform:** Douyin Web only (`douyin-web.adapter.ts`)
- **Product:** Chrome extension + FastAPI + Celery workers
- **Includes:** Single video → batch → visual → export → production hardening (56 tasks)
- **Excludes:** Phase 5 (multi-platform, teams, comparison) unless user explicitly requests

V1 complete = task **P6-18** `done`.

## Non-Negotiable

- User-triggered capture only — no silent recording
- Structure over copying — no script clones
- Browser-assisted — not headless crawling
- Validate all LLM JSON before DB save
- Update BACKLOG + STATUS when finishing a task

